Text: RE Im Leaving EnronGood luck to you and I hope our paths cross again Glynda A Becker Legislative Director Representative Mark R Kennedy Original Message From mailto Sent Friday March PM To Becker Glynda Betfarhad Ramsen KADDENCOM kaddencom Cabasco Vergil WPPCorg Devon Kehoe TomO PAgov ernercom judy WPPORG MCIMAILCOM Subject Im Leaving Enron I am going to be the Senior Regulatory Counsel at ISO New England starting on April My last day in the Portland area will be March I enjoyed working with you and wish you the best of everything My new address will be Mary Hain Senior Regulatory Counsel ISO New England Inc One Sullivan Road Holyoke MA SONEcom
